35
00:01:42,314 --> 00:01:45,884
Okay, so to understand carbon
dating we have to understand that

36
00:01:45,909 --> 00:01:51,163
normal carbon that we have is carbon-12,
but cosmic rays hit the earth and

37
00:01:51,188 --> 00:01:56,601
