nitrogen 14 to become carbon-14.

38
00:01:56,626 --> 00:01:58,399
Now where is this nitrogen 14?

39
00:01:58,399 --> 00:02:01,829
Oh, nitrogen is in the air — an
enormous percentage is nitrogen-14.

40
00:02:01,854 --> 00:02:05,940
So cosmic rays hit that,
convert that to carbon-14.

41
00:02:05,965 --> 00:02:10,120
So now we have two types of carbon:
normal carbon which is carbon-12,

42
00:02:10,145 --> 00:02:14,128
