radioactive element— to decay by half.

76
00:03:58,954 --> 00:04:04,997
So in carbon-14 you’re looking
at 5,730 years as a half-life.

77
00:04:05,022 --> 00:04:11,506
So what that means is: imagine
you have this amount. After
5,730 years it halves itself.

78
00:04:11,531 --> 00:04:12,076
Okay.

79
00:04:12,101 --> 00:04:17,132
