those nitrogen-14 atoms, right?

196
00:10:14,234 --> 00:10:15,042
Yes, that’s right.

197
00:10:15,067 --> 00:10:17,280
But when we have a
stronger magnetic field

198
00:10:17,305 --> 00:10:20,843
— and we know that we had a much
